Name: Aztec Number
About the game: Challenge puzzle masters from all over the world Accompanied by powerful sound effects, solve 108 puzzles and take possession of the secret treasure of the Aztecs. How to Play Clear the stages by tracing the blocks in the order of the numbers that are displayed on the right. Before tracing the blocks, you can click as many times as you have MOVE and move the blocks anywhere you want.
